<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1093730/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1093730-20.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1093730/" class="author">
